cu.explanation_en: Setting the AMF IPv4 address to an invalid format '999.999.999.999' will cause AMF connection failures and prevent proper core network communication.

du.explanation_en: Setting the downlink carrier bandwidth to an invalid value of 999 will cause frequency configuration errors and prevent proper downlink channel setup.
du.explanation_zh: 將下行鏈路載波頻寬設定為無效值 999 會導致頻率配置錯誤，並阻止正確的下行鏈路通道設定。
